"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1979546-olympics-daniel-wiffen-kneecap-concert\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Olympicsace Daniel Wiffen has issued a statement after claims he'd joined Irish hip-hop band Kneecap on stage while wearing a balaclava.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 76, \"end\": 81, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9415240133768256, \"rank\": 0.053375991929007646, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 95, \"end\": 102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patella\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6790984280825766e-24, \"text\": \"Kneecap\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\", \"Q265868\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patella\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen was one of several standout performers for the Irish Olympics team at the Paris Games this summer, taking two medals in the swimming pool.\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 285, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9415240133768256, \"rank\": 0.053375991929007646, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after a video from Kneecap's gig in Bristol, which appeared to show a man climbing up on stage while wearing a medal, went viral this week, Wiffen has been forced to respond.\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patella\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6790984280825766e-24, \"text\": \"Kneecap\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\", \"Q265868\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patella\"}, {\"begin\": 327, \"end\": 334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bristol\", \"score\": 0.5567389477726842, \"rank\": 0.7956620251986504, \"text\": \"Bristol\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bristol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bristol\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taking toInstagram, the 23-year-old said: \\\"Hi All.\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is currently a video trending on social media claiming to be me in attendance at a Kneecap Concert in Bristol (UK).\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patella\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.6790984280825766e-24, \"text\": \"Kneecap\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\", \"Q265868\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patella\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Patella\"}, {\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bristol\", \"score\": 0.5567389477726842, \"rank\": 0.7956620251986504, \"text\": \"Bristol\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bristol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bristol\"}, {\"begin\": 635, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9997599790690649, \"rank\": 0.0002365361906310682, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the video it claims to be me, to be invited on stage wearing a balaclava / facemask and then to participate in a rap song.\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For clarification this was not me on stage and I was not in attendance at that concert.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay safe Daniel.\\\"\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen earned plenty of plaudits for his exploits in Paris, taking gold in the 800m freestyle, before backing it up with bronze in the longer 1500m event a couple of days later.\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999997755631082, \"rank\": 2.244367838224993e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being born in Leeds and attending Loughborough University, Wiffen moved to County Down in Northern Ireland at age two and chose to represent the Irish swimming team.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds_United_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9506099935423483, \"rank\": 0.05182546414375964, \"text\": \"Leeds\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds_United_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds_United_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loughborough_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.977338268221115e-14, \"text\": \"Loughborough University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loughborough_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loughborough_University\"}, {\"begin\": 1155, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999905046248091, \"rank\": 9.495459748693322e-06, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1210, \"end\": 1215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9415240133768256, \"rank\": 0.053375991929007646, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes from Northern Ireland can choose whether to represent Team GB or Ireland.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1248, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999905046248091, \"rank\": 9.495459748693322e-06, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9998674023392942, \"rank\": 7.414330771313217e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1308, \"end\": 1315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9997805670478251, \"rank\": 0.00012779980497965086, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wiffen developed cult status during the Games, specifically for his witty post-race interviews.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Commenting after the 10,000m open water swim event, Wiffen told Irish broadcaster RTE: \\\"When I got to halfway, all I was thinking was 'I am already Olympic champion and I am swimming this and I am coming 18th, we will just finish it now and then I am never doing it again.\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9415240133768256, \"rank\": 0.0533759919290